# thoth_tenant_settings

Manages default tenant policy posture, webhook routing, SIEM/PAM configuration, secret broker controls, and model router defaults.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_tenant_settings" "tenant" {
  compliance_profile = "soc2"
  shadow_low         = "allow"
  shadow_medium      = "step_up"
  shadow_high        = "block"
  shadow_critical    = "block"

  webhook_enabled = true
  webhook_url     = var.webhook_url
  webhook_secret  = var.webhook_secret
}
```
